dct_description_sm: Appears in: Gentleman's Magazine or Monthly Intelligence, vol. 1, 1731. London, F. Jeffery.
Map includes Europe, Asia and the Far East. The oval-shaped cartouche contains a floral border with a female face wearing a wide-brimmed hat.
